background\"><\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-label\">TOOLS<\/div><div class=\"post-info__item-value\">ADOBE AFTER EFFECTS, ILLUSTRATOR, PHOTOSHOP, dragon frame, CINEMA 4D<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/header><div class=\"t-box-b post-detail__body\"><nav class=\"post-detail__tabs\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-dot is--active\"><\/div><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab is--active\">OVERVIEW<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">CHALLENGE<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">REFLECTION<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab false\">AWARD<\/div><\/ul><\/nav><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body\"><ul class=\"post-detail__tab-body-list\"><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item is--active\">To create a fun, simple yet complex branding targeted for potential Ringling PreCollege students<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">We wanted to develop branding across print and motion celebrating typography, mix media, all that one can imagine to learn when young. How do we achieve combining all these mediums but giving a tactile feel?<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">By delegating tasks and trusting the team through meetings, we were able to pull through and have a cohesive successful branding! <br>We hoped the students love what we came up with \ud83d\ude00<\/div><div class=\"post-detail__tab-body-item false\">ADDY Professional Silver Award (Cross-Platform, Integrated Campaigns<\/div><\/ul><\/div><div class=\"post-detail__media-container\"><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/PC_1.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/PC_1.webp\" alt=\"\"\/><\/picture><picture class=\"post-detail__media-image\"><source media=\"(max-width:600px)\" srcset=\"https:\/\/jasminegunarto.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/12.5.webp\"\/><img decoding=\"async\"